                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960914-20-off115 t17960914-20-cd116"></join>, a leather thread-case, value 4s. 6d. a penknife, value 4d. a pair of scissars, value 8d. and a pair of tweezers, value 1d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17960914-20-victim328" type="victimName">
